citations:
    citation-adwd-jon-i:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "Jon I"
            text_from_source: "Stannis Baratheon had smashed Mance Rayder's host and made the King-Beyond-the-Wall his captive … but the wildlings were still out there, the Weeper and Tormund Giantsbane and thousands more."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Jon Snow as Lord Commander. Stannis Baratheon is at Castle Black with his army after defeating Mance Rayder. Jon deals with Stannis's demands and hears Alliser Thorne's complaints about the legitimacy of his election. Stannis intends to burn Mance. Jon argues Mance would be more useful alive. Stannis wants to grant wildling lands south of the Wall, which Jon opposes. Val is mentioned as a wildling princess held at Castle Black."
